four years ago.

38:26.753 --> 38:28.030
No shit.

38:28.417 --> 38:29.911
Parents from Atlanta.

38:29.985 --> 38:33.247
Friends with Mrs. King,
Dr. Cosby, Rev. Jackson.

38:33.313 --> 38:34.655
