53:25.158 --> 53:27.067
What is your problem with him anyways?

53:27.141 --> 53:29.628
Besides the fact, of course, that he's white.

53:29.701 --> 53:33.246
You gonna get in a heap of trouble
talking to me like that.

53:33.540 --> 53:36.957
