being white. He's hiding something.

53:37.030 --> 53:38.436
What? NASCAR?

53:39.781 --> 53:41.754
You thought I didn't know?

53:42.085 --> 53:45.914
Of course I knew.
We talk about everything, Simon and I.

53:47.556 --> 53:50.971
Daddy, I love him,
and you need to start respecting that.

53:51.396 --> 53:54.842
Then you respect me enough to tell me
in advance who you're bringing home.

53:54.915 --> 53:57.282
- I didn't think you'd care.
- But you weren't sure.

53:57.347 --> 53:59.486
- So you decided to test me.
- No, of course not.

53:59.556 --> 54:01.116
