01:04:39.417 --> 01:04:40.693
Hey, baby!

01:04:41.433 --> 01:04:44.150
Theresa! Come here, sweetheart.
Daddy needs to talk to you.

01:04:44.218 --> 01:04:46.867
- Don't listen to him.
- What are you talking about?

01:04:46.937 --> 01:04:50.351
