01:06:04.338 --> 01:06:07.918
- You hear that? "You people."
- I know. I heard. What people?

01:06:08.947 --> 01:06:10.801
The people in the yard.

01:06:13.555 --> 01:06:16.522
That's what I'm... See?
I say one thing and I'm a racist!

01:06:16.595 --> 01:06:19.377
- No, Simon, you're a liar.
- And a racist.

01:06:20.274 --> 01:06:23.405
Where do you get off calling me a racist?
I have a black girlfriend!

01:06:23.473 --> 01:06:25.774
- You had a black girlfriend!
- Have.

01:06:25.841 --> 01:06:28.362
Past tense! Had!
